flowchart LR
    P0["Phase 0<br/>Two hours of driving<br/>Voice-in works; replies are unreadable"]
    P1["Phase 1<br/>Research<br/>OSS, TTS economics, iOS constraints"]
    V1["Phase 2 · v1 ghost<br/>Native full duplex<br/>Mic complexity; background unverified"]
    R["Phase 3 · Raven v2<br/>Reframe to voice-out only<br/>Remote Control keeps voice-in"]
    A["Phase 4<br/>Stop hook → Kokoro → continuous HLS<br/>Tailscale → native iPhone player"]
    PROOF["First proof<br/>Playback survives background + screen-off"]
    B["Phase 5<br/>Driving-led build-out<br/>Channels, transcript, mute, catch-up"]
    G["Phase 6<br/>Go migration<br/>hook + serve + write + diagnose"]
    BUGS["Phase 7<br/>Live corrections<br/>double-speak · exit 137 · prompt pollution"]
    NEXT["Phase 8<br/>Current frontier<br/>sentence-streamed synthesis"]
    LATER["Later / higher risk<br/>latest-wins · sentence cuts · live narration"]

    P0 --> P1 --> V1
    V1 -->|"delete unnecessary mic ownership"| R
    R --> A --> PROOF --> B --> G --> BUGS --> NEXT --> LATER

    V1 -. claimed proof without evidence .-> PROOF
    P1 -. Kokoro local economics .-> A
    P1 -. background capture differs from playback .-> R

